{
  "id": "63ed99fb29f5c7001b0e5d9b",
  "title": "コップに半分水がある",
  "created": 1676515853,
  "updated": 1679041610,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63ed99fb29f5c7001b0e5d9b",
      "text": "コップに半分水がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676515853,
      "updated": 1676515853
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9cbfaff09e0000755017",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/6740e7576c92a3cdca804b2e6c5227a3]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516543,
      "updated": 1676516547
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9cc3aff09e0000755018",
      "text": "[半分水が入ったコップ]を見て考えることが人によって違う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516547,
      "updated": 1676516624
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9cedaff09e0000755019",
      "text": "　A: コップに[半分しか水がない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516589,
      "updated": 1676516628
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9a0caff09e00006c845c",
      "text": " B: コップに[半分水がある]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676515853,
      "updated": 1676516636
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9a13aff09e00006c845e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676515860,
      "updated": 1676515860
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9d3faff09e000075501f",
      "text": "広く知られている[たとえ]だと思う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516671,
      "updated": 1679040788
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9d1daff09e000075501b",
      "text": " この[たとえ]話の初出はどこだろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516637,
      "updated": 1676516673
    },
    {
      "id": "641422d1aff09e00002816e5",
      "text": " [Quote Investigator https://quoteinvestigator.com/2022/04/06/half-full/]によれば誰が最初かは不明、見つかった最も古いものが匿名であるため",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679041236,
      "updated": 1679041409
    },
    {
      "id": "64142314aff09e00001f8ffe",
      "text": "\t >Quote Investigator: The earliest match found by QI appeared in “The Evening Sun” of Baltimore, Maryland in April 1929. The statement occurred in a filler item without attribution. Boldface added to excerpts by QI:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679041300,
      "updated": 1679041356
    },
    {
      "id": "64142314aff09e00001f8fff",
      "text": "  >[* If he says his gas tank is half-full he’s an optimist. If he says it’s half-empty he’s a pessimist.]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679041301,
      "updated": 1679041359
    },
    {
      "id": "6414235aaff09e00001f9001",
      "text": "  (DeepL)ガソリンが半分入っていると言えば、楽観主義者だ。もし半分しかないと言うなら、彼は悲観主義者だ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679041370,
      "updated": 1679041389
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9d38aff09e000075501d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516665,
      "updated": 1679041416
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9d20aff09e000075501c",
      "text": "イメージしやすいたとえ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516640,
      "updated": 1676516843
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9debaff09e0000755022",
      "text": "　だが、コップで100%が規定されてしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516843,
      "updated": 1676516851
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9df3aff09e0000755023",
      "text": "　その結果、暗黙に「100%を目指すのが良い」(コップに水を入れるのが良い)という判断を導いてしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516851,
      "updated": 1676516855
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9d57aff09e0000755020",
      "text": "　「コップに水を入れるのが良い」という考えは[不足に注目する]行為",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516695,
      "updated": 1676517027
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9da9aff09e0000755021",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516777,
      "updated": 1676516777
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9dfeaff09e0000755024",
      "text": "[足るを知る]的な意味で使われることもある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516863,
      "updated": 1676516894
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9e1daff09e0000755026",
      "text": "　その場合[不足に注目する]ことが、[成長への欲求]を生み出すのではないか、不足に注目しなければ成長しないのでは、という批判が成り立つ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516894,
      "updated": 1676516989
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9e7faff09e0000755027",
      "text": "　[理想と現実のギャップ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516991,
      "updated": 1676517003
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9e00aff09e0000755025",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676516864,
      "updated": 1676516864
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9e94aff09e00006c845f",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676517012,
      "updated": 1676517015
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9e97aff09e00006c8461",
      "text": "\t[不足に注目する人]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676517015,
      "updated": 1676517022
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9e96aff09e00006c8460",
      "text": "　　このたとえが発展したもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676517015,
      "updated": 1676517044
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9eb4aff09e0000755029",
      "text": "　　ただし抽象度は上がっている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676517045,
      "updated": 1676517058
    },
    {
      "id": "63ed9eafaff09e0000755028",
      "text": "　[ドラッカー]がこれに関したことを言ってる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676517039,
      "updated": 1679041433
    },
    {
      "id": "641423a8aff09e00001f9002",
      "text": "　\t>6. Changes in Perception",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679041449,
      "updated": 1679041449
    },
    {
      "id": "641423a9aff09e00001f9003",
      "text": "  > “The glass is half full” and “The glass is half empty” are descriptions of the same phenomenon but have vastly different meanings. Changing a manager’s perception of a glass from half full to half empty opens up big innovation opportunities.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679041449,
      "updated": 1679041449
    },
    {
      "id": "6414238caff09e00002816e6",
      "text": "\t\t2002年[https://hbr.org/2002/08/the-discipline-of-innovation The Discipline of Innovation]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679041420,
      "updated": 1679041480
    },
    {
      "id": "6414238caff09e00002816e7",
      "text": "\t\t(DeepL) コップが半分入っている状態から半分空になっている状態へと、マネージャーの認識を変えることで、大きなイノベーションの機会が生まれます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679041420,
      "updated": 1679041535
    },
    {
      "id": "641423ffaff09e00001f9005",
      "text": "\t\tこれは「半分空だ」と認識する方が有益だと言ってる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679041536,
      "updated": 1679041569
    },
    {
      "id": "64142421aff09e00002816e9",
      "text": "\t[2人の靴のセールス]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679041570,
      "updated": 1679041610
    },
    {
      "id": "63eda03aaff09e000075502d",
      "text": "[二人が違うことを言う絵のシリーズ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676517434,
      "updated": 1676517438
    },
    {
      "id": "63eda03baff09e000075502e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676517435,
      "updated": 1676517435
    }
  ]
}